---
title: Loaded Lentil Chili-Cheese Potato Wedges with Avocado and Sour Cream
description: Tonight, we're turning lentils into the vegetarian version of a pub classic, featuring roast potato wedges,  avocado, sour cream, and the always delicious cheddar cheese.
